reviewText: If you like the idea of naked men with each other putting you to sleep. . . no not to bed to SLEEP get this DVD!!!!!!!!!!

It's not actualy porn and it's not actualy an entertaining movie. I must have missed the point. No story line, no romance, no reach around. I usually have good things to say but this was a poor investment.

That Jason Jordan has it exactly right. This is a homo-epic of astounding proportions, as indeed were one or two of the delicious young men in the movie. I'd give this thousands of stars if I could, because that's all I can see after playing along with this DVD for 10 minutes or so...

When I saw this dvd i thought that it would be good. Judging from the cover and reading about it it seems as if there would be a lot of sex and possibly a threesome. NOT!! The scenes switch off from one to another right in the middle and later come back. I wouldnt put this on the top of the A or B list.
This is a great movie. I was really taken by the actions and thought put into it. Its not the best I have ever seen, but its definitely one you should watch. Get this and be suprised!!
